project_descr: "Rada za Evropu: Capacity-Building in Support of the Verkhovna Rada of Ukraine (VRU)" aims to strengthen the VRU capacity  to produce quality legislation and monitor its implementation to serve as a  driving force for reforms.

outputs.output_descr: Strengthened capacity of the Verkhovna Rada of Ukraine to produce quality legislation and monitor its implementation to fulfil its Constitutional prerogatives and to serve a model and a driving force of the reforms.
